sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Client
    participant ConfigModule as ConfigModule
    participant Daemon
    participant SHM as SharedScheduler(SHM)
    participant Queue as JobQueue
    participant Worker

    Note over Client,Daemon: Startup Phase
    
    Client->>ConfigModule: config_load(config_file)
    ConfigModule->>ConfigModule: parse socket_path, num_workers
    ConfigModule-->>Client: config (or defaults on error)

    Daemon->>ConfigModule: config_load(config_file)
    ConfigModule-->>Daemon: config
    Daemon->>SHM: shm_scheduler_create()
    Daemon->>Daemon: fork_workers(config.num_workers)
    Daemon->>Daemon: ipc_server_listen(config.socket_path)

    Note over Client,Daemon: Command Phase
    
    User->>Client: minisched_client ADD "echo hello"
    Client->>Client: ipc_client_connect(socket_path)
    Client->>Daemon: send "ADD echo hello"
    
    Daemon->>Queue: job_queue_push(job)
    Daemon->>SHM: history_jobs append(PENDING)
    Daemon-->>Client: "ENQUEUE JOB ID[1] DONE"
    Client-->>User: ID 1 added
    
    Daemon->>Worker: pthread_cond_signal()
    
    Worker->>Queue: job_queue_pop()
    Worker->>SHM: state = RUNNING, pid = getpid()
    Worker->>Worker: system(command)
    Worker->>SHM: state = DONE/FAILED, exit_code

    Note over Client,Daemon: Status Query
    
    User->>Client: minisched_client STATUS
    Client->>Daemon: send "STATUS"
    
    Daemon->>SHM: scheduler_stats_update()
    Daemon-->>Client: TOTAL=1 | DONE=1 | FAILED=0 | RUNNING=0 | PENDING=0
    Client-->>User: display job table

    Note over Client,Daemon: Shutdown Phase
    
    User->>Client: minisched_client STOP
    Client->>Daemon: send "STOP"
    
    Daemon->>SHM: shutting_down = 1
    Daemon->>Worker: pthread_cond_broadcast()
    Worker-->>Daemon: exit (all workers)
    
    Daemon->>SHM: shm_scheduler_destroy()
    Daemon-->>Client: "STOPPING DAEMON"
    Client-->>User: daemon stopped